idatha enkulu: Amasethi wedatha amakhulu kakhulu ukuthi angacutshungulwa ngokwesiko

ukuthuthukiswa kwewebhu: Ukwakha nokugcina amawebhusayithi nezinhlelo zokusebenza zewebhu
ukuthuthukiswa emuva: I-logic yohlangothi lweseva nokuphathwa kwedatha yewebhusayithi
umbono wekhompyutha: Ivumela amakhompyutha ukuthi 'abone' futhi aqonde ulwazi olubonakalayo
